    "en": {
      "title": "The Chinese ship arrives",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "China's experimental ship Yuan Wang 5 has arrived at Hambantota port. This ship arrived at Hambantota port to get fuel and essential services.",
        "The Chinese Embassy has also organized a ceremony at Hambantota port this morning to welcome the ship.",
        "India as well as America expressed their objection regarding the arrival of this ship to Sri Lanka, and then they failed to present reasonable reasons for it, so the government gave the required permission for the ship to arrive at Hambantota.",
        "This ship was supposed to arrive in Sri Lanka on the 11th. However, Sri Lanka made an official request to the Chinese Embassy to delay that date."
      ],
